In this video, I dive into the unexpected world of tech products available on SHEIN, testing everything from knockoff gaming consoles to bizarre phone cases. Along the way, I encounter some truly head-scratching items, like "AirPods" with a screen and a game console power bank combo. While most products fell short of expectations, there were a few surprising finds that might just be worth your time.
